{"iti20:0.1":"Itivuttaka 20 ","iti20:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","iti20:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","iti20:0.4":"Padutthacittasutta ","iti20:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti20:2.1":"“Idhaham, bhikkhave, ekaccam puggalam padutthacittam evam cetasa ceto paricca pajanami: ","iti20:2.2":"‘imamhi cayam samaye puggalo kalam kareyya yathabhatam nikkhitto evam niraye’. ","iti20:2.3":"Tam kissa hetu? ","iti20:2.4":"Cittam hissa, bhikkhave, paduttham. ","iti20:2.5":"Cetopadosahetu kho pana, bhikkhave, evam’idhekacce satta kayassa bheda param marana apayam duggatim vinipatam nirayam upapajjanti”ti. ","iti20:2.6":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti20:2.7":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti20:3.1":"“Padutthacittam natvana, ","iti20:3.2":"ekaccam idha puggalam; ","iti20:3.3":"Etamatthanca byakasi, ","iti20:3.4":"buddho bhikkhuna santike. ","iti20:4.1":"Imamhi cayam samaye, ","iti20:4.2":"kalam kayiratha puggalo; ","iti20:4.3":"Nirayam upapajjeyya, ","iti20:4.4":"cittam hissa padusitam. ","iti20:5.1":"Yatha haritva nikkhipeyya, ","iti20:5.2":"evamevam tathavidho; ","iti20:5.3":"Cetopadosahetu hi, ","iti20:5.4":"satta gacchanti duggatin”ti. ","iti20:6.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti20:6.2":"Dasamam. ","iti20:6.3":"Dutiyo vaggo. ","iti20:7.0":"Tassuddanam ","iti20:7.1":"Moho kodho atha makkho, ","iti20:7.2":"Vijja tanha sekhaduve ca; ","iti20:7.3":"Bhedo samaggipuggalo, ","iti20:7.4":"Vaggamahu dutiyanti vuccatiti. "}